    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has visible wear and some minor rust spots. The interior shows signs of regular use and has several noticeable stains. All mechanical components are functional, though they show typical wear for a car of this age.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine runs consistently and the transmission shifts through all gears, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and typical engine noise for a car of this era. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there are a few electronic quirks, such as a temperamental window motor and an aged infotainment screen. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and the need for ongoing maintenance.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle presents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning motorist. Exhibiting consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, the specimen offers a refined driving experience that aligns with our dealership's rigorous standards. Each component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure sustained performance and reliability. We invite you to experience the superior road presence and mechanical poise of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, super clean, and drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. You\u2019re going to love how it handles\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus. This unit delivers linear power delivery and remains oil-tight. The G96 six-speed manual gearbox provides tactile, short-throw shifts, paired with a recently refreshed clutch and a proactive IMS bearing upgrade. The suspension geometry is dialed in, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for neutral cornering and precise feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the structural and mechanical integrity is paramount, making this an ideal high-performance analog machine.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Reliable performance. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the ideal balance between a high-end driving experience and everyday reliability. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin has been smoke-free and meticulously kept; the leather seats show light softening but no tears, and all power features, including the sunroof and premium audio system, operate perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection confirming that the brakes and tires have plenty of life left. It is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium feel without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle presents a sophisticated balance of performance and value. It has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the interior remains refined and well-preserved, catering to the driver who demands excellence without the premium of a showroom-new price point. An exemplary choice for those seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been well-loved and runs like a dream. It's in great shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a quintessential example of high-revving atmospheric performance. At its heart is the S54 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently calibrated dual-VANOS system for optimal torque delivery across the powerband. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that ensures predictable power distribution. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings to preserve the integrity of the multi-link rear geometry. While the exterior reflects its history as a dedicated driver\u2019s tool, the mechanical vitals are synchronized perfectly, offering the communicative hydraulic steering and balanced weight distribution that defined an era of motorsport-derived engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
